// math.t2f - Fixed point math library for t2f
// All values scaled by 1000 (so 1.0 = 1000, -1.0 = -1000)
// sin/cos tables cover 0..359 degrees

// Fixed-point sine table (degrees 0-89, scaled by 1000)
// Full sin(x) computed via quadrant mirroring in fp_sin
